<item>
<title>Anandamurti</title>
<link>http://www.livingwithbaba.net/articolo/art0498.htm</link>
<description>Baba has explained clearly the real meaning and glory of the name of &#34;Shiva&#34; and &#34;Krsna&#34;. Sadhakas should understand why Baba is called Anandamurti and what the real form of Anandamurti is. However, neither do I have the intellectual nor the spiritual capacity to explain to you His real form as Anandamurti. All I can say is that He is the embodiment of love and devotion.</description>
